sentences: Vrangsinn (Birthname Daniel Salte) is a Norwegian musician, best known as the bassist of Carpathian Forest (1999–2014/2019–present).
Vrangsinn is the president of Misantrof ANTIRecords, a non-profit organization he established in 2007.
